SD=Credit Risk Models
CR=Credit Risk Model Specification
BQs=Production Testing FunctionalRequirements
This service domain handles the development, maintenance and continual assessment and refinement of the collection of credit models that are deployed across the bank. This includes individual credit assessments and more complex analyses for merchants and companies/corporations. The models are used to derive credit scoring and support more involved credit analysis/insight development
A credit model is used to analyze product activity in order to refine then banks credit assessment of a customer
This service domain handles the design and maintenance of a portfolio of credit models that are used in all aspects of customer credit assessments
CR - Credit Risk Model Specification							BQ - Testing				BQ - Production				BQ - Functional Requirements			
In	Up	Co	Ec	Ca	Rq	Re	Up	Ca	Rq	Re	Up	Ca	Rq	Re	Up	Ca	Rq	Re
InCR Instantiate a new Credit Risk Model Specification
UpCR Update details relating to Credit Risk Model Specification
CoCR Control the processing of Credit Risk Model Specification
EcCR Accept, verify, etc. aspects of Credit Risk Model Specification processing
CaCR Capture Credit Risk Model Specification activity or event related information
RqCR Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Credit Risk Model Specification
ReCR Retrieve details about any aspect of Credit Risk Model Specification
UpBQ Update details relating to Testing
CaBQ Capture Testing activity or event related information
RqBQ Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Testing
ReBQ Retrieve details about any aspect of Testing
UpBQ Update details relating to Production
CaBQ Capture Production activity or event related information
RqBQ Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Production
ReBQ Retrieve details about any aspect of Production
UpBQ Update details relating to Functional Requirements
CaBQ Capture Functional Requirements activity or event related information
RqBQ Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Functional Requirements
ReBQ Retrieve details about any aspect of Functional Requirements